		<div id="post_message_1173732">
                  
                  <div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
	<tr>
		<td class="alt2" style="border:1px inset">
			
				<div>Originally Posted by <strong>Vista</strong></div>
				<div style="font-style:italic">Regarding the first sentence:  If you mean dps in the short term then I and probably everyone else (or the vast majority) agrees with this statement.  Sorcerers definitely have the mantle of best burst/fast damage of all casters.  They should not have excessive superiority in damage in any long term case (if any advantage) though.  And perhaps should not have too much of an advantage against druids in the medium time frames.<br />
